  "text": "In our evaluation, we measured the number of packets, the size of transferred data and web loading time to access a web site. The former two results are measured at the access point using tcpdump. The web loading time is the elapsed time from when a user clicks the load button to when the progress bar of the browser hits 100% [CITATION_1] . To measure the web loading time, the browser was modified to record time stamps for its internal operations.",
